# How to merge PDFs using Quick Actions

## Reference
- [How To Merge PDF Files On Your Mac](https://youtu.be/cKhTaPEqNDI?si=WvRstcX2nQoIS4nz), macmostvideo

## Merge PDFs using Quick Actions
- Select multiple files in Finder.
- Right-click to get the context menu.
- From Quick Actions, select Create PDF